some kind of shrine.

26:54.323 --> 26:55.246
UNABOMBER...
Theodore Kaczynski Arrested and...

26:55.281 --> 26:56.198
Bundy Claims...
Police Believe The Number To Be...

26:56.233 --> 26:57.621
Cannibal Killer
DECAPITATED UNABOMBER

26:57.656 --> 27:01.115
