is torn out of his calendar.

27:44.152 --> 27:46.322
That's tomorrow.
What happens tomorrow?

27:47.159 --> 27:50.284
- Hold on. Hold on.
- Get out of there, Oddie.

27:50.319 --> 27:53.076
