out a way to entrap him.

27:59.035 --> 28:01.951
So, what's in it?
Is he a mass murderer?

28:01.986 --> 28:03.279
No.

28:05.576 --> 28:07.416
But I think he wants to be.

28:07.451 --> 28:11.113
Hey, Bob!
Robert, where the hell are you?

28:11.410 --> 28:13.815
I want my gun back!

28:19.119 --> 28:21.110
Oh, shit. Damn dogs.

28:23.619 --> 28:25.077
Shut up, you hear me?

28:29.661 --> 28:31.085
Shut up you damn dogs!

28:31.120 --> 28:34.319
One of these days, bang!
You hear me?

28:40.995 --> 28:43.620
