28:50.495 --> 28:52.058
Been communing with the dead?

28:52.093 --> 28:54.000
It's not about who's dead, sir.

28:54.035 --> 28:55.907
It's about who soon might be.

28:58.496 --> 29:00.336
We call him Fungus Bob.

29:00.371 --> 29:03.496
Yeah, I saw him enter the grill, but
he didn't strike me as suspicious.

29:03.531 --> 29:05.670
