to walk a dangerously narrow line.

29:15.781 --> 29:19.122
That's just because I've got such
great respect for your balance, sir.

29:19.157 --> 29:21.806
Son that sounds perilously close
to being bullshit.

29:21.841 --> 29:24.455
There's a little bit of
bullshit in it. A little.

29:24.490 --> 29:26.504
