29:51.332 --> 29:53.624
It's like cleaning fluid
with sugar in it.

29:53.659 --> 29:55.339
Which reminds me, how's your dad?

29:55.374 --> 29:59.332
He's selling pieces of the moon
online, vacation home sites.

29:59.367 --> 30:00.255
Is that legal?

30:00.290 --> 30:02.791
