32:40.126 --> 32:40.973
We will be.

32:41.008 --> 32:43.508
Oh, I guess I didn't think
"Let's put a pin in it" meant "Yes. "

32:43.543 --> 32:46.009
You have to learn to listen
with more than just your ears.

32:46.043 --> 32:48.710
